body_html: I had 2 versions of Python installed. One basic version of Python and one installed by Anaconda. When running my machine learning script it threw the same error. When I uninstalled one of the two versions (in my case I removed Anaconda) everything works fine again. I use deeplearning4j as library and apparently it has difficulties to resolve this dll, cause there were multiple Python installations installed.
